You will work within a fast-paced Agile DevOps team contributing and collaborating within your scrum team on a daily basis.
Build scalable web solutions from Proof of Concept (POC).
You will enhance web applications and APIs.
Collaborate with architects, product owners and subject matter experts to design and implement technical solutions.
Participate in Scrum events required in Agile software development environment.
