Perform analysis, design, coding, testing, implementation, and maintenance of software solutions;
Collaborate with stakeholders to design and launch new features;
Provide digital strategy and execution in the form of websites, native applications and other related technologies;
Create and maintain technical documentation for design and implementation details; and
Work with agile teams to refine requirements and to identify areas for enhancement.
